parameters.toolDescription:
Creates a custom table with user-specified name and fields. For advanced users who want additional tables.

{
  "name": "Bookings",
  "fields": [
    {"name": "Name", "type": "singleLineText"},
    {"name": "Phone Number", "type": "phoneNumber"},
    {"name": "starttime", "type": "dateTime", "options": {"dateFormat": {"name": "european"}, "timeFormat": {"name": "24hour"}, "timeZone": "utc"}},
    {"name": "endtime", "type": "dateTime", "options": {"dateFormat": {"name": "european"}, "timeFormat": {"name": "24hour"}, "timeZone": "utc"}},
    {"name": "eventid", "type": "singleLineText"},
    {"name": "Service", "type": "singleLineText"},
    {"name": "Status", "type": "singleSelect", "options": {"choices": [{"name": "confirmed"}, {"name": "cancelled"}, {"name": "completed"}]}},
    {"name": "Notes", "type": "multilineText"}
  ]
}

For create_custom_table:
- date fields MUST have: "options":{"dateFormat":{"name":"iso"}}
- dateTime fields MUST have: "options":{"dateFormat":{"name":"iso"},"timeFormat":{"name":"24hour"},"timeZone":"utc"}
- number fields MUST have: "options":{"precision":0} or 2
- singleSelect MUST have: "options":{"choices":[{"name":"Option1"}]}
